Implements DnD for /admin/crm using @dnd-kit/core and @dnd-kit/sortable:
- draggable user cards across 8 columns
- optimistic UI updates and server update on drop
- error rollback with toast on failure
- visual cues: drag overlay, opacity, shadow, and destination highlight
- column droppable handling and constraints (no intra-column moves)
- maintain existing structure and protections (Admin route)

